{"type": "article", "id": 60507, "title": "五芳斋展示“国民年夜饭”，雅芳抗橘皮组织产品广告惹争议 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-22T05:10:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5503, "name": "新年"}, {"id": 2399, "name": "支付宝"}, {"id": 26515, "name": "五芳斋"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190122125223A3eTfY1QIvn7wj2C.jpeg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p line=\"u9Mb\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4330932615733628?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>故宫和好想你合作推出两款“枣有心意”和“颜禧饮膳”礼盒，</b></a>还推出联名卫衣，正反面连起来正好是“好想你”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125249Y8tgysESU5TH3oln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125253TAxhtVz80gUGwoXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125255ML5FTtAUpQJHkV1s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125254bJ3lFvLsaXuYy6rp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125346zx0IaqNFiGE7oeMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"7Jro\"><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/54263209.html?weibo_id=4330991088342918\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>支付宝昨天发布了五福新年广告“七里地”</b></a>，选择了传统的春节习俗“福”字，讲述祖孙三代人无论怎样的境况，都会和“福”字紧密联系在一起。结尾回到现代生活，提醒观众扫五福活动将要开始了。该片由许鞍华导演，演员金士杰和春夏主演。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b083079zsah\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"b00g\">微信过年发红包有了新变化，<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NTE4Njc4NQ==&amp;mid=2657617414&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d9edbd57596a8f6f3b4caffe84d217fa&amp;chksm=bd60f7088a177e1eff8967414169b11f265fad1aad69023ef6ab10663567e3c0426339831a38&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0122evoBfDEkXjtN4R3NK40I&amp;key=c1e117273d7b427602fc4df44141e26a024f656fab4fe0edb0dbd99921429fe5253b5c84de36441f8379794cdba74014901165849e013ae5cfa56226d9e9a38b4dd505887f23b8beed66a7ecd89fafde&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=prRJfWl9EgrlukVeLeLeQvzq5MBn6Bzk88%2FzSUoeAFeXeUb0Y3JUwHlMzrTwTjgc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>企业微信认证的企业，可以定制自己喜欢的红包封面，</b></a>然后通过“企业微信通知”或者二维码将红包封面发送给员工。部分出境游玩的用户，也能获得境外受邀商家发送的定制封面。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125421YjiyzwkG5ro67xbK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600601\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125421FJ54E0O8jRmPi2xT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"cRsE\"><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/54160297.html?weibo_id=4330846800469313\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>五芳斋的春节广告将场景定格在了民国时代，展现了当时准备年夜饭的场景。</b></a>这次制作方环时互动，购买了周璇演唱的《五芳斋》作为背景音乐。</p><p line=\"ubV6\">片中隐藏了许多彩蛋，路人鲁迅，麻将桌边的阮玲玉，还重现了电影《马路天使》的情节等等。不过结尾告诉观众这依然是卖货的广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=a08298be55i\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"3FP8\" class=\"\">五芳斋同时还发布了一组人物海报和静物海报。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125520sFlzfqNSdRUC3702.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125521q8oU4lS9n1OcP6ey.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125520SeM98vlrpHTQoGqu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125522pzDwqrlLaF0NxYgb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901221255222IJjFxHNEXMqoaP1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125522oqvEu1Xmn6bVSwJz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125523JlLKFC9VZMnAyDSH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125523yRoAXjSLtliJFM65.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125523mUtLWf9BJbEiKMvw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"RBjN\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NDA3MjMxNg==&amp;mid=2652123233&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7dc8152c15f5d395da8b4fc78e7a136c&amp;chksm=8bb4acf2bcc325e4ec167f1ffe154cd5eb9a724cc566988257deab8a4a46032ec2abf951ac5a&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0122BzBpd8QMVs2tOPP2UshC&amp;key=d3a191f9ed1cc3b262426ac1a25090fb8653f47d545615bf5a66a3e47407e37a20a5dd32aa021483b95f68911980401412352df5231bb53c1c5cb47d8c7462d9d5c557ec99b3b02ec2053709e851e552&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=prRJfWl9EgrlukVeLeLeQvzq5MBn6Bzk88%2FzSUoeAFeXeUb0Y3JUwHlMzrTwTjgc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>众安保险推出的新年广告聚焦在农历猪年这一意象，</b></a>故事从猪八戒踏上去往天竺的列车讲起，不过一路上的经历并没有那么如意。值得一提的是，部分场景由 86 版猪八戒扮演者马德华出演。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w08301tva99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"xkz0\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/v4FRmRHi_5I\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>虎牌啤酒马来西亚地区发布的新年广告 “uncages new beginnings”，</b></a>主题没有刻意强调团圆，男孩想成为文身师，可是父亲却希望他继承家族企业，不过最终理解了他的坚持。整体节奏都把握得不错。创意代理商来自奥美马来西亚。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0830f6dla4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"IMf6\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/6934569935/4330278925620818\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>腾讯最近在上海月星环球港养鸡了</b></a>。由《鬼吹灯》小说改编的第三季电视剧《怒晴湘西》昨天上线，这之前腾讯专门从剧中故事发生地湘西农村找来 10 只公鸡，放到洒满米的巨大玻璃“养鸡场”中。当鸡把米啄完，下面隐藏的播放信息也露出了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125657P4adKFYno8G2kvx7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125657L9YGwcpuI46mjAK1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125657RvKpVQMSdWjowhCI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125658Dg0jtbFUYnGePLhC.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"jv69\" class=\"\">英国奢侈品百货公司 Harrods和潘通合作推出&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.harrods.com/en-gb/the-art-of-colour/pantone/silver?icid=theartofcolourpantonelaurelwreath_colour-navigation_module-24_element-1_silver\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“The Colour of Art”（艺术的颜色）活动，</b></a>选择了 9 种充满温柔气息的潘通色，Harrods 推荐同色系商品销售。线下橱窗也同步同色系单品展示。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012212571720dMSXnNcG6osRV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901221257174YwghyjJKFrbE1V9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125718Oa2NobIxzYecfvS0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190122125718jrMWwzUShFxTGue1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019012212571871U8iwDteEGbnrcI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666309\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"ycKP\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2019/01/21/avon-pulls-anti-cellulite-campaign-its-accused-abusing-body-positive-movement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">根据 The Drum 报道，</a>雅芳推出一款减少身体橘皮组织的产品，即解决有些女性身材发胖后，臀部会出现脂肪团的问题。广告语“Dimples are cute on your face.Not on your thighs.”（你脸上的酒窝很可爱，但你大腿上的可不是。）</p><p line=\"daM2\">英国女演员 Jameela Jamil 认为这些现象是女性年龄增长不可避免的，因此在推特上指责雅芳羞辱女性的年龄和伴随而来的衰老状态。雅芳最终在推特上为自己的问题广告道歉，并且撤销了相关的营销材料。</p><p line=\"daM2\" class=\"\">题图来自：五芳斋</p>"}